      <title>交易员在美国期权市场追逐选举后的股票涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/traders-chase-post-election-stock-gains-us-options-market-2024-11-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[期权投资者正在美国股市上大举押注风险更高的股票，支撑股市上涨，因为大选忧虑逐渐消退，且预计共和党明年将掌控华盛顿的大权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/traders-chase-post-election-stock-gains-us-options-market-2024-11-15/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Nov 2024 06:03:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>百时美施贵宝因抗癌药物延期上市再次面临 67 亿美元诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/bristol-myers-faces-renewed-67-bln-lawsuit-over-delayed-cancer-drug-2024-11-14/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，百时美施贵宝公司遭到一起 67 亿美元的诉讼，指控其欺骗了 Celgene 的前股东，推迟了三种药物的联邦批准。一个半月前，联邦法官突然驳回了该案件的早期版本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/legal/bristol-myers-faces-renewed-67-bln-lawsuit-over-delayed-cancer-drug-2024-11-14/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 23:49:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据《巴伦周刊》报道，花旗集团因与受制裁的俄罗斯亿万富翁的关系而面临美国调查</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/citigroup-facing-us-probe-over-ties-sanctioned-russian-billionaire-bloomberg-2024-11-14/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《巴伦周刊》周四援引知情人士的话称，花旗集团因与受到制裁的俄罗斯亿万富翁苏莱曼·阿布萨多维奇·克里莫夫的关系而受到美国政府机构的调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/citigroup-facing-us-probe-over-ties-sanctioned-russian-billionaire-bloomberg-2024-11-14/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Nov 2024 22:11:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
